{"word":"στενακτός","slug":"στενακτός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>στενακτός</b></el> <el>(στενακτός, ή, όν) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:στενάζω'><el>στενάζω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to be mourned, giving cause for grief</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>mournful</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}